0:13:09.820,0:13:15.440
I can't actually recollect my age but I was very young.

0:13:15.440,0:13:18.600
We had seniors. It was like a system.

0:13:18.600,0:13:29.600
So, they told me that I was one year old when they took me to the shrine.

0:13:29.640,0:13:38.000
