0:14:30.360,0:14:33.200
so that I too would become a senior.

0:14:33.200,0:14:44.880
In my case, I prayed in my language, 'Evineva lo', which means, 'Let somebody come'

0:14:44.880,0:14:48.100
because I was tired.

0:14:48.140,0:15:01.900
