0:19:46.020,0:19:50.700
the person would be severly punished.

0:19:50.740,0:19:56.700
But for me, that wouldn't enter my head because I needed food to eat.

0:19:56.700,0:19:59.300
I needed food at all costs.

0:19:59.360,0:20:06.100
